Fresh Design is a development agency with main focus on business process automation through implementation of online services for the business to communicate with its clients. 
We specialise at:
lead management systems; 
marketplace development;
MDM-systems;
integration platforms;
partner interaction platforms for retail and b2b.
Based in Ukraine, we have representatives in Netherland, USA and Germany. 
Some of our clients - Danone (France), British American Tobacco, Reckitt Benckiser (GB), Alfa-Bank (Ukraine), VTB (Russia), Nemiroff (Ukraine) and many other.
How everything is done:
We have our own business automation platform called fdForge, which is the basis that helps us launch solid complex projects in a short term period.
 
